<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Country Hills</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A rapidly growing residential community in the north-west quadrant of Calgary, Country Hills offers a serene family friendly surrounding ideal for both raising your children and spending a peaceful and enriching life post-retirement. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">With its abundant green spaces, countless recreational facilities, excellent public amenities and charming environment, the community in Country Hills is fast becoming a hot favorite real estate destination for homebuyers and investors alike. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">One of the major attractions in the neighborhood is the humungous Country Hills golf course that bisects the community into two and provides plenty of open spaces for both children and adults to enjoy their leisurely hours amidst nature.</p>

        </div>
